machine_start_gcode.default_value:
;MachineType:TINA2S
;FilamentType:{material_type}
;Extruder0Temperature:{material_print_temperature}
;BedTemperature:{material_bed_temperature}
;InfillDensity:{infill_sparse_density}
;(**** start.gcode for tina2s****)
M203 Z5 ;Move Z axis up 5mm
M117 Homing axes
G28 Z; Home extruder axis Z
G28 X Y; Home extruder axis X Y
M117 Start Warm Up
M140 S{material_bed_temperature} ;start heating the bed to what is set in Cura
M104 S130 ;start heating E to 130 for preheat
M190 S{material_bed_temperature} ;Wait for Bed Temperature
M117 Levling the build plate
G29
G1 Z1.0 F3000 ;Move Z Axis up to 1mm
G1 X0.5 Y1 ;Move hotend to starting position
M117 Heating Hotend
M104 S{material_initial_print_temperature} T0 ;start heating T0 to what is set in Cura
M109 S{material_initial_print_temperature} T0 ;Wait for Hotend Temperature
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
M117 Purging and cleaning nozzle
G1 X1.1 Y10 Z0.28 F1000.0 ;Move to start position
G1 X1.1 Y90.0 Z0.28 F2000.0 E15 ;Draw the first line
G1 X1.4 Y90.0 Z0.23 F5000.0 ;Move to side a little
G1 X1.4 Y10 Z0.20 F2000.0 E15 ;Draw the second line
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
G1 Z2.0 F3000 ;Move Z Axis up
G1 X1 Y5 Z0.2 F5000.0 ;Move over to prevent blob squish
M117 Printing...

machine_end_gcode.default_value:
;(**** end.gcode for tina2s****)
M203 Z15 ;Move Z axis up 5mm
M104 S0 ;Turn off extruder heating
M140 S0 ;Turn off bed heating
M107 ;Turn Fans off
G92 E0 ;(Reset after prime)
G0 E-1 F300 ;Retract Fillament 1mm
G28 Z F300 ;Park Hotend up
G28 X0 Y0 ;Park Hotend
G1 Y90 F1000 ;Present finished model
G0 E-2 F300 ;Retract Fillament 2mm
M82 ;absolute extrusion mode
M104 S0 ;Ensure hotend is off
M117 Print Complete
